Omenugha kwuru na ụlọakwụkwọ ga-etinye onyoko IP n'ụlọ ule na rụkwaa tebul obosara enweghị akpa ime maka nnyochagharị ntozu
Dịka o kwuru, atụmatụ a na-arụgara aka ịkụda ohi ule n'etiti ụmụakwụkwọ na ndị nkuzi
"Ebe onyoko IP ga-egosi ihe ọbụla mere n'ụlọ ule, tebul obosara enweghị akpa ime ga-eme ka ụmụakwụkwọ hapụ iwepụta ihe ọbụla ezighi ezi n'ụlọ ule ahụ," Omenugha kwuru
Ọkammụta Omenugha tinyere that iji akwụkwọ ndabanye nke ụlọakwụkwọ edebanye ụmụakwụkwọ maka ule abụrụla nke agbanwere ma were mbinye bayometrik ụmụakwụkwọ nọchie anya ya
